    "display_name": "Content Creator",
    "long_instructions": "## Carla Rivas, Digital Content Creator\r\n\r\n**Location:** Madrid, Spain\r\n\r\n**Workplace:** Freelance, Social Media Influencer\r\n\r\n**Expertise:** Tech reviews, fashion trends, wearable tech marketing\r\n\r\n**How I Use AI:** \"I showcase the Jacquard Smart Jacket to my audience, demonstrating how wearable tech enhances daily life. My content helps people see how AI-powered fashion is changing the way we interact with technology.\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:\r\n   * Key roles and responsibilities\r\n   * Key challenges\r\n   * How computing supports their work\r\n   * How your chosen innovation helps their job\r\n2. Summarize key insights in your activity guide.",
